<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>시험 결과 - 경찰청 통합 진급 사이트</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .result-box {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .score {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #007bff;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .home-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 18px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        .home-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>시험 결과</h1>
        <div class="result-box">
            <h2>총점</h2>
            <div class="score"><%= score %>점</div>
            <p><%= message %></p>
        </div>
        <a href="/" class="home-button">홈으로 돌아가기</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 